## Limitations

The analysis is based on available data and reports, which may not capture the most recent developments in global health funding. Additionally, the economic estimates provided are subject to change based on global economic conditions and policy decisions. The moral and ethical considerations, while discussed, are inherently subjective and may vary across different cultural and political contexts.